                    <p>Bri's role extends beyond traditional operations management. She bridges the gap between strategic vision and tactical execution, translating the company's ambitious goals into actionable plans. Her ability to see the big picture while managing critical details has been essential to iSN.BiZ's reputation for reliability and excellence in enterprise software delivery.</p>
