                    <p>Bri has implemented cutting-edge project management methodologies that have improved delivery times by 35% while reducing operational costs. Her data-driven approach identifies bottlenecks before they become problems and continuously refines processes based on real-world performance metrics. This commitment to continuous improvement has made iSN.BiZ exceptionally efficient and responsive.</p>
                    <p>She has pioneered the integration of automation tools and AI-assisted workflows that free the team to focus on high-value activities. From automated testing pipelines to intelligent resource allocation systems, Bri's innovations ensure that iSN.BiZ operates at peak efficiency without sacrificing the human touch that clients value.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Bio Content Row 3 -->
            <div class="bio-row">
