                    <p>Beyond systems and processes, Bri is deeply committed to building a strong organizational culture. She has developed onboarding programs, mentorship initiatives, and professional development pathways that attract and retain top talent. Her belief that operational excellence starts with engaged, empowered team members has created a workplace where people thrive.</p>
                    <p>Bri's collaborative leadership style encourages open communication and cross-functional cooperation. She has broken down silos between development, design, and business teams, creating a unified organization where everyone understands their role in delivering exceptional client outcomes. This culture of collaboration has become a competitive advantage for iSN.BiZ.</p>
