                    <p>While operations is her primary focus, Bri maintains close relationships with key clients to ensure their needs are understood and met. She personally oversees quality assurance processes and client communication protocols, ensuring that every interaction reflects iSN.BiZ's commitment to excellence. Her attention to detail and proactive approach has contributed significantly to the company's perfect client retention rate.</p>
                    <p>Bri understands that in the software industry, reliability is as important as innovation. Clients trust iSN.BiZ because they know Bri's operational systems will deliver consistently excellent results. This trust has led to expanded relationships, referrals, and long-term partnerships that form the foundation of the company's success.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Bio Content Row 5 -->
