                    <h3>Technology & Systems Expertise</h3>
                    <p>Bri maintains deep technical knowledge that informs her operational decisions. She understands software architecture, development methodologies, and emerging technologies, enabling her to make informed decisions about tooling, infrastructure, and process design. This technical fluency allows her to bridge the gap between engineering teams and business stakeholders effectively.</p>
                    <p>She has led the implementation of modern DevOps practices, cloud infrastructure management, and security protocols that protect client data while enabling rapid development cycles. Her ability to balance innovation with stability has been crucial as iSN.BiZ scales to handle larger, more complex enterprise projects.</p>
