                    <p>Beyond day-to-day operations, Bri is passionate about thought leadership in operational excellence. She believes that the software industry can learn much from manufacturing's lean principles and is pioneering approaches that combine agile methodologies with rigorous operational discipline. This unique perspective positions iSN.BiZ as an innovator not just in technology, but in how technology companies operate.</p>
